For a number of years, film exhibitors voted Chandler among the top stars at the box office.
* 1952 – 22nd (US)
* 1953 – 18th (US)
* 1954 – 16th (US)
* 1955 – 20th (US), 7th (UK)
* 1956 – 18th (US), 5th (UK)
* 1957 – 22nd (US), 6th (UK)

