<doc id="1136964" wikidata="Q3282535" url="?curid=1136964" title="One Foot in the Blues">
<text>One Foot in the Blues is a compilation album by the American rock band ZZ Top, released in 1994 (see 1994 in music). The album contains a selection of the band&#x27;s songs which fall into the blues genre. With the exception of the songs taken from the &quot;Degüello&quot;, &quot;El Loco&quot;, &quot;Eliminator&quot; and &quot;Recycler&quot; albums, the 1987 digital remixes were used.

==Track listing==
