# &quot;Where&#x27;s the Manual?&quot; – 5:23
# &quot;Senseless Fun&quot; – 4:39
# &quot;Bad Seed&quot; – 4:02
# &quot;Incredible&quot; (Carter, Easdale) – 4:18
# &quot;Prayer&quot; – 4:37
# &quot;Don&#x27;t Feel Like Doing Drugs&quot; – 3:43
# &quot;Right On Baby, Baby&quot; – 4:23
# &quot;Late Night Phone Call&quot; – 5:32
# &quot;28 Double Secret Bonus Tracks&quot; – 5:35

