<doc id="1137034" wikidata="Q2821603" url="?curid=1137034" title="Abibatou Traoré">
<text>Abibatou Traoré (born 1973) is a Senegalese writer and a member of the &quot;Eminent Minds&quot; panel created by Secretary General Kofi Annan. This panel was created to make suggestions for the fundamental reformation of the United Nations as an institution.

==Works==
